&lt;li&gt;You will also work on broader custom quantitative and qualitative projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With input from your manager, you will be writing questionnaires, testing survey links, and ensuring data integrity throughout the research process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be responsible for data analysis and reporting, identifying key trends and insights.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will interrogate the findings, helping to craft compelling presentations alongside senior team members.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will have a strong focus on specific therapeutic areas and collaborate directly with the client to support their brand planning and strategic development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will also play a key role in supporting the Director in running workshops, helping client teams translate research insights into strategic brand development and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your job will involve mentoring and managing junior team members, ensuring best practices and knowledge sharing within the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
