&lt;p&gt;This role is critical to scaling the scripting function and de-risking the transition from outsourced delivery to a blended / in-house model. It combines hands-on complex scripting with technical governance, quality ownership, team coaching, process development, capability-building and stakeholder advisory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will help build confidence that the India team can deliver increasingly complex scripting requirements to the required quality standard while reducing dependency on external vendors.&lt;/p&gt;
