&lt;li&gt;You will write proposals, identifying opportunities for growth and contributing to revenue generation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will also help shape team strategy and ways of working, ensuring alignment with broader organisational objectives and best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
